        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You dance, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Stride]{Striding} up to half your Speed. At either the start or end of your Stride, you create an area of magical darkness in a 10-foot burst centered on your location. This area is filled with magical darkness that works the same way as that created by a @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Darkness]{Darkness} spell of the same level. When you create the darkness, attempt a Performance check to dance, with a standard DC for your level, to determine the duration of the darkness.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong>: 1 minute</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong>: 2 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong>: 1 round</p>"
